<div id="push">
<section id="section-6">
      <h2 id="name-push"><a href="#section-6">6.&nbsp;&nbsp;Push</a></h2>
<p id="section-6-1">Servers <span class="bcp14">MUST</span> support the JMAP push mechanisms, as specified
in <span>[<a href="#RFC8620" class="cite xref">RFC8620</a>], <a href="https://rfc-editor.org/rfc/rfc8620#section-7" class="relref" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Section 7<span class="u-visually-hidden"> (opens in new window)</span></a></span>, to allow
clients to receive notifications when the state changes for the Quota type
defined in this specification.<a href="#section-6-1" class="pilcrow">¶</a></p>
</section>
</div>
